{
  "stem": "10588.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We would give them-- we'd get like 50 ores, which is like $0.50 here, to buy-- just pocket money.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So I would give them the money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They would buy us the things that we, in mute language, we try to show them, they would buy it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then one time when I learned how-- a little bit, this young man said to me, when I get out, he wants to take me out for a date.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I didn't know who he is, what he was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And when we went out on the date, the first thing he said to me, you don't look like Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And I felt like a knife twisted in my heart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I said, here, I suffered as a Jew, and I survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it's supposed to be a compliment that I'm not who I am.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I didn't wait for him to say anything more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I started to run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And I ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Never will I see him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Then there was in the-- in [SWEDISH], was a woman, a rabbi's wife, who survived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Her name was Rebbetzin Dukush.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Rabbi's-- that's how we used to call it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "Dukush was her name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But she was a rabbi's wife.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "D-U-K-- D-U-K-U-S-H.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "S-C, or S-H, something like this here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she wanted-- she was interested for the young children to continue to have a Yiddish education.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So anyone who was under 21, she offered to take to a kosher lager.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A lager is a camp, again, so-- but this was like a DP camp, still.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I volunteered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But trouble was, she would not take Bina.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said to her, Mrs.-- Rebbetzin Dukush, how can you separate me-- this is-- this is to me like a sister.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
